{"tid":2154554,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽誤會我入左Poly","createTime":"2020-08-13T07:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T18:47:05.000Z","uid":116235,"like":21,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4c5443a038130b63b83f4c15a6928e5d64f461","tid":2154554,"uid":116235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日JUPAS放榜<br />\n我考得太好，但又怕呀媽周圍哂命<br />\n所以出左DSE成績都無同佢講咩分數<br />\n之後仲偷偷地報左美國既大學<br />\n呀媽一生人既夢想我入三大<br />\n因為佢d親戚街坊都無仔女入到三大<br />\n<br />\n今日一早起身，呀媽係咁問我第幾志願，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間U<br />\n我是但同呀媽講我入左理工，<br />\n之後就入房訓覺(尋晚通頂打丁)<br />\n<br />\n岩岩起左身，屙完屎之後出黎<br />\n發現成家人都死老豆咁既樣，呀爸呀媽叫哂佢d親戚姑嫂話今晚出黎食飯<br />\n話要安慰我入左Poly 都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n依個時候先知大撚獲<br />\n我其實係入麻省理工學院 MIT<br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係香港，理工即係Poly<br />\n所以呀媽以為我剩係入左Poly<br />\n<br />\n屌你<br />\n呀媽仲問我第時出黎係咪去做地盤<br />\n我都唔知點答佢好..."},{"pid":"0f1d4375ba13c675edaa9c43d1527f5a874239b0","tid":2154554,"uid":215734,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:49:21.000Z","msg":"師兄ho ball😂"},{"pid":"f3131d719022cc5f1c981a2f38da444be627ca6b","tid":2154554,"uid":51715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"ha"},{"pid":"6b67a71c6f12443d4ec42aa37c744249ee8d28f7","tid":2154554,"uid":214594,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"Gag講多就唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6473c74c515302ff72f868f6652ec37e99fcfd2a","tid":2154554,"uid":332452,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"想識樓主"},{"pid":"4802f8894eee77e555ee02b9c177946cada89673","tid":2154554,"uid":305553,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ad93b4cf4600c3063d8790caa446a8b518cc5c7","tid":2154554,"uid":336070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"屌博到我一笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class